title: Day 709
content:
# Day 709

Happy leap year! I was asked to put to bed my Daughter so I did then I ended up asleep. Came back out to write and read but man did I want to keep sleeping.

I'm so blessed to be a Dad. That's it. That is the post. Procreate more. Have children. Believe me it will change your life for the better. 10x increase :)

2/29/24

Conor Jay Chepenik
